    "name": "Verduran Ambush",
    "prerequisite": "*Verduran Shadow Dedication*; expert in *Stealth*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You prepare to ambush a foe. You Ready an activity that takes 2 actions, though that activity must either be Death from Above or an activity with the requirement that you be hidden or undetected by all your opponents (such as Scout\u2019s Pounce). After using the reaction, you cannot use this feat again for 10 minutes.",
